snippet.title: beatmania CORE REMIX (Arcade / 2000) - Gameplay
snippet.description:
beatmania CORE REMIX, emulated via MAME 0.182 (using the new PortAudio output module).

1:18 Remixed by TATSUYA NISHIWAKI (Original Music by reo-nagumo) - Do you love me? FINAL EDIT (SOUL)
3:31 Remixed by SLAKE (Original Music by prophet-31) - 2 gorgeous 4U EMULATE MIX (BREAK BEATS)
5:27 Remixed by SLAKE (Original Music by MIRAK) - OVERDOSER FLOTAGE MIX (TECHNO)
7:16 Remixed by QUADRA (Original Music by QUADRA) - Beginning of life THE GROUND PULSE MIX (TECHNO)
9:46 Remixed by TATSUYA NISHIWAKI (Original Music by n.a.r.d.) - 20,november FINAL EDIT (HOUSE)
11:58 Remixed by YUKIHIRO FUKUTOMI (Original Music by Lovemints Unlimited Orchestra) - love's theme of beatmania (CROSSOVER)
14:06 Remixed by KEN MATSUMOTO (Original Music by THE BALD HEADS) - SKA a go go SKA CORE MIX (SKACORE)
16:05 Remixed by SLAKE (Original Music by DJ FX) - Acid Bomb LATINIZE MIX (LATIN HOUSE)
18:15 Credits

Let me know if there are any specific songs you want to see.  Will probably do another video for this game, to highlight the new (non-remixed) tracks.

https://remywiki.com/AC_bm_CORE_REMIX
